name: Earth Defender (Deliriny2020)
description:
Hey everyone welcome to the end of the world!

Just like in the dinosaur age, the world is coming to an end because of a meteor.

or rather, meteors.

Defend the earth in wave after wave of defending the earth from meteors to delay, not stop, the end of the world. 

Laser Go pow pow

Have a good day!
